p.k: The Titans put on a show but Robin warns that the performance must be boring or else they'll wake up the wolves. / After not receiving participation medals, the Titans must demonstrate what they learned at camp. / Bumbleebee becomes the 6th Titan and moves into the Tower but has a hard time adjusting. / Bumblebee offers to help Robin with his leadership skills by teaching him how to act like a queen bee. / Needing a hero with shrinking powers, but forgetting about Bumblebee, Robin invites The Atom to join their fight against the Brain.
